			<h2>Enter the Bay Foundation…</h2>
			<p class="content offset">
				Clearing the urchins has allowed the kelp forests to regrow, 
				which in turn has benefited all kinds of native marine life
				— including the malnourished purple urchins.
			</p>
			<p class="content offset">
				The results have been instantaneous and astounding...
